#!/usr/bin/env glas

Hi.

Welcome to The Glas Language. 

This is still a concept, therefore not to be used directly.

Use this as a stub file for decorating all glas compatible scripts.
Also, other glas elaborations like Wordy, and many many more.

Enjoy!

# Pure glas section
{! glas !}
stop: -> glas

# Wordy Glas section
{! glas.wordy !}
stop: ->  wordy ->> glas

# Glas Styks section
{! glas.styks !}
stop: -> glas ~ styks

